failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lvh1665702711625.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lvh1665702711625.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lvh1665702711625.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lvh1665702711625\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Database I/O Translation\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Indicates whether data strings should be translated on database input and output.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lvh1665702711625__section_w212ab1b5b1_w213ab1b5_w214ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"lvh1665702711625__table_d677e1_d678e1_d679e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lvh1665702711625__table_d677e1_d678e1_d679e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lvh1665702711625__table_d677e1_d678e1_d679e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lvh1665702711625__table_d677e1_d678e1_d679e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Not defined</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lvh1665702711625__table_d677e1_d678e1_d679e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No data is translated</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lvh1665702711625__table_d677e1_d678e1_d679e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">N</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lvh1665702711625__table_d677e1_d678e1_d679e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No data is translated</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lvh1665702711625__table_d677e1_d678e1_d679e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Y</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lvh1665702711625__table_d677e1_d678e1_d679e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Data is translated using the translation tables defined for the field's parent component.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lvh1665702711625__section_dpv_tth_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1233814e136\">Applies to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"lvh1665702711625__ul_e1l_5th_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lvh1665702711625__li_d3698e1_d3699e1_d3700e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yzg1665702711012.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yzg1665702711012.html\" title=\"A Modeled Field Interface is a Development Object that defines a reusable value for the Database Interface property of a Database Field.\">Modeled Field Interface</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dsd1665702981243.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Database Translation Tables</a><p>Database translation tables convert character strings during database input or output. This makes it possible to display characters stored in the database that are normally not visible (such as typesetting codes), or to store a key entered in a field as another string.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529749\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529749\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Database I/O Translation Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Database I/O Translation Indicates whether data strings should be translated on database input and output. Value Description Not defined No data is translated N No data is translated Y Data is translated using the translation tables defined for the field's parent component. Applies to Modeled Field Interface Related Links Database Translation Tables Database translation tables convert character strings during database input or output. This makes it possible to display characters stored in the database that are normally not visible (such as typesetting codes), or to store a key entered in a field as another string. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}